{"tid":149561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10漢夜盜宋代古墓 吸入毒氣4死","createTime":"2017-03-09T11:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T16:01:51.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f31043f61de5275ea5bcb58d3b784cb3f78dfbe4","tid":149561,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>【邪！】10漢夜盜宋代古墓 吸入毒氣4死<br />\n</strong><br />\n2017-03-09 18:11:42 HKT  <br />\n<br />\n前日凌晨，10名盜墓賊在盜掘貴州習水縣程寨鎮一座宋代古墓時，因吸入有毒氣體，4人死亡，多人入院就醫。據了解，被盜掘的古墓為縣級文物。<br />\n<br />\n據習水縣政府網通報，共有10名男子參與盜墓。事發後，墓內有3名男子當場死亡，另一重傷者送醫後搶救無效死亡，其餘4名輕傷者經搶救情況穩定，另2名「把風」男子被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被盜的古墓2001年公佈為習水縣第一批縣級文物保護單位，墓主身份不詳，但確定為宋代墓葬。此前，曾多次遭破壞和盜墓賊光顧。前晚，記者在程寨鎮的案發現場看到，盜墓賊在墓後部耕地裡挖出的盜洞，已經被泥土封填，恢復原狀。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，盜墓賊在此已打下了一個深約8米的洞，欲通向墓內。但在掘進中，他們可能遇到了石頭，試圖破壞時，在洞內使用了燃油發電機，並在洞口鋪了棉被以阻隔聲音傳出，結果導致空氣不流通，有毒氣體在洞內聚集。<br />\n<br />\n這座具有明顯宋墓石刻的古墓位於村子的一個角落，前方是一座多年無人居住的破土房。距離古墓最近的人家，直線距離不足百米。據住在古墓附近的兩位老人說，他們晚上睡覺很早，並沒聽到怪聲。"},{"pid":"6406862b0d6dbddc41c16a268a129a602a09adc2","tid":149561,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"在洞內使用了燃油發電機，並在洞口鋪了棉被以阻隔聲音傳出，結果導致空氣不流通，有毒氣體在洞內聚集。"},{"pid":"d9f8b33a025bc246f3411e215313d2cbfcbb5f80","tid":149561,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"冇相關知識都起碼睇本鬼吹燈先落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06d844eb5a78311eec9496624d42a091879ac77","tid":149561,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇相關知識都起碼睇本鬼吹燈先落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入去第一件事係東南角點蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd219e49d09a25f6c74130eeb108e00fddb6c5a","tid":149561,"uid":90123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"睇盗墓筆記大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bda7cd9294ee0fb4ac581dae90383b837ce146","tid":149561,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafea494daab5d9e627ee1164766fca39e5795d0","tid":149561,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇相關知識都起碼睇本鬼吹燈先落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5984f9c0fbc3493c006604f8c32a14729c55dd31","tid":149561,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59050ca2238be0d9650d2d2feb1e0dd0d6750d62","tid":149561,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"大陸人係咪個個都認為自己百毒不侵"},{"pid":"76aabe7e6ebe33cad038db386980cc4e1e3c63d7","tid":149561,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇相關知識都起碼睇本鬼吹燈先落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入去第一件事係東南角點蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天王蓋地虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑驢蹄子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be50492dfb8e8e3fe6520b7fb0e08873beaeafe","tid":149561,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"原來係自己毒死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e9b2ecbf2387fb39ee5b6c8b6221c5f0216166","tid":149561,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":